{"tid":374884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做完激光矯視，你問我答","createTime":"2017-08-26T05:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T12:23:55.000Z","uid":20973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"76f957cb85a75d98ce83f238af4234cddb00ba99","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"琴日做<br />\n做lasik <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e15fddc4101d1c8c53604bddb5a7e17a32ca6d","tid":374884,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3232af1fcd8a2e766fca1b05124e760670139e81","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>how much</blockquote><br />\n養和做<br />\nPackage $22000<br />\n但我自己揀醫生，淨手術費$27000"},{"pid":"cfe02af7c24649ec9abe8d93ae0487748a08ac7d","tid":374884,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"why not smile?"},{"pid":"5bc3d05e9abdb3caa56d0bd391c3b2986ebcebc7","tid":374884,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"巴打 我做完3個月啦 可以打籃球 游水了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2477006ebf0e391c458a9dfae3151ce988062297","tid":374884,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 我做完3個月啦 可以打籃球 游水了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過我係香矯做 18500"},{"pid":"f128254aa266c10940dbbfc2fe1dcd1c5d12d768","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>why not smile?</blockquote><br />\n做之前問左眼科醫生朋友<br />\nSmile係新技術<br />\n理論上唔洗整flap,會冇flap complications<br />\n但始終技術係香港唔成熟<br />\n冇prolong data<br />\n會唔會過幾年之後有rebound myopia未有人知住<br />\n<br />\n今日覆診問埋醫生<br />\n佢話其實都要整flap,只係唔洗lift up<br />\n而lasik打完laser之後d野自己evaporate走<br />\nSmile打完laser要由醫生dissect層layers出理再拎走佢<br />\n所以smile係冇咁準<br />\n同埋lasik部機你隻眼郁，部機會trace返你隻眼<br />\n但smile部機係唔會<br />\n如果smile係真係有佢地講到咁好既話養和一早引入左<br />\n同埋而家只係第一代<br />\n佢地覺得冇added benefit仲要冇咁準"},{"pid":"8738f97942ae84640f499f1aad35101f3d0497f7","tid":374884,"uid":708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"做完要唔要休息下幾日先返到工之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6252b7aaa5e76814fd5903b24a93662cda21ec","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做完要唔要休息下幾日先返到工之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗<br />\n不過第二日要覆診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da7b4e326a512f88be37af26bd818b7c328adab","tid":374884,"uid":10334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0d7059ecfc66b074696d1f81adbbf09f8769f8","tid":374884,"uid":126268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"師兄,有散光可以做嗎"},{"pid":"300fcb0038d3d665a762120ed233ec6d6e0de835","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄,有散光可以做嗎</blockquote><br />\n可以<br />\n我都有散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343922a8147d96320949118f0e4d4ab017b01861","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d41a8f7f8fae29c89f555fcece2561e85e33f2","tid":374884,"uid":118721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"我都做左幾年。<br />\n<br />\n而家深左50度外咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n但我18000<br />\n唔是醫院做<br />\n想問下巴打點解選擇醫院？"},{"pid":"b552d900a800e000149815939e68e6d7bc81090a","tid":374884,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9fbfb940aeebe7c979c01b4a13a695912bb6ec16","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都做左幾年。<br />\n<br />\n而家深左50度外咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n但我18000<br />\n唔是醫院做<br />\n想問下巴打點解選擇醫院？</blockquote><br />\n錢對我哩講唔係concern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要係安安全全，做得好<br />\n我相信養和咁大間醫院點都好啲既<br />\n同埋問過身邊做左既人<br />\n除左2個係診所做之外其他都係哩到做"},{"pid":"c3fd9c48cc81d88dc77e7b49e5461fb7a64d1047","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"不過其實只要搵位日日做，夠熟手既醫生就ok<br />\n而且lasik主要都係靠部機做<br />\n所以診所定醫生都無乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己揀哩位醫生係因為做手術時間岩我<br />\n同埋有好多醫師朋友都係搵佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話佢特別好<br />\n只不過係一個做完覺得ok之後再介紹比其他人"},{"pid":"9fb5f62fe31fb05451c14a386ce63602156149e3","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過其實只要搵位日日做，夠熟手既醫生就ok<br />\n而且lasik主要都係靠部機做<br />\n所以診所定醫<span style=\"color: red;\">院</span>都無乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己揀哩位醫生係因為做手術時間岩我<br />\n同埋有好多醫<span style=\"color: red;\">生</span>朋友都係搵佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話佢特別好<br />\n只不過係一個做完覺得ok之後再介紹比其他人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e034ec705e32f4890ecba935725b784ff3bd3878","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcbc7b72a0a08702d6ec3f274b75f2649bf3714","tid":374884,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"有冇後遺症?<br />\n聽過話做完唔可以玩機動遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋做完近視又深番有冇得再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691b36d3d7c9337821edf8a72dfb5d40404469df","tid":374884,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"有D 想做 但想做smile <br />\n夠快 又細傷口"},{"pid":"b2a7ef4cf3fba45e48aafb2f19904b4eb5dc8026","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇後遺症?<br />\n聽過話做完唔可以玩機動遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋做完近視又深番有冇得再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做完一日咋所以有冇後遺症未知住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問過人多數話頭幾個月會眼乾<br />\n夜晚塞車要小心d因為會有halo<br />\n機動遊戲應該玩得喎<br />\n<br />\n近視深返如果cornea夠厚可以再做"},{"pid":"fec7474cc9e21cb6c6b51ecdde2da6354e3f1473","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有D 想做 但想做smile <br />\n夠快 又細傷口</blockquote><br />\n想做就做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12f4bb68b6fec7883477116f899af794b703b4a","tid":374884,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇後遺症?<br />\n聽過話做完唔可以玩機動遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋做完近視又深番有冇得再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做完一日咋所以有冇後遺症未知住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問過人多數話頭幾個月會眼乾<br />\n夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">揸</span>車要小心d因為會有halo<br />\n機動遊戲應該玩得喎<br />\n<br />\n近視深返如果cornea夠厚可以再做</blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1252ab9307bb400fbc96790b7b7f3dc6426bea3","tid":374884,"uid":68600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"巴打過左幾耐清晒？ <br />\n我琴日做完 睇野冇帶眼鏡果陣咁清，醫生話會慢慢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}